								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[10-Feb-2020 19:03:34 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[11-Feb-2020 15:20:40 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,

[11-Feb-2020 19:21:39 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[11-Feb-2020 19:21:39 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

							 FROM `tbl_product`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[12-Feb-2020 15:54:47 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_id` = 15 || `PG`.`group_id` = 15) AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[12-Feb-2020 15:54:47 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[12-Feb-2020 17:58:15 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

							 FROM `tbl_product`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[28-Feb-2020 12:16:52 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[03-Mar-2020 19:36:09 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_id` = 15 || `PG`.`group_id` = 15) AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[14-Mar-2020 17:46:54 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_code` LIKE '%mesh%' OR `tbl_product`.`title` LIKE '%mesh%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_type` LIKE '%mesh%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_key` LIKE '%mesh%' OR `PR`.`title` LIKE '%mesh%' OR `GP`.`title` LIKE '%mesh%') AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;

							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[14-Mar-2020 22:06:11 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[24-Mar-2020 14:40:06 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[26-Mar-2020 18:11:39 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[27-Mar-2020 18:53:54 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[27-Mar-2020 18:54:39 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[28-Mar-2020 13:43:21 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[31-Mar-2020 16:53:12 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[31-Mar-2020 17:06:28 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[31-Mar-2020 17:08:26 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[31-Mar-2020 18:16:59 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[31-Mar-2020 22:21:08 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
[31-Mar-2020 22:21:12 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[02-Apr-2020 21:21:29 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[02-Apr-2020 21:21:29 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[03-Apr-2020 19:12:22 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[03-Apr-2020 19:12:22 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[03-Apr-2020 19:15:09 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[03-Apr-2020 19:15:09 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[04-Apr-2020 13:32:23 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[04-Apr-2020 13:32:23 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[04-Apr-2020 14:17:30 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[04-Apr-2020 14:33:49 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[04-Apr-2020 14:37:01 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_id` = 36 || `PG`.`group_id` = 36) AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[05-Apr-2020 21:39:41 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[05-Apr-2020 22:00:23 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[07-Apr-2020 20:34:06 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[08-Apr-2020 13:55:04 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`

[08-Apr-2020 18:29:38 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[08-Apr-2020 18:30:16 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[17-Apr-2020 13:46:11 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[17-Apr-2020 13:46:11 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[17-Apr-2020 13:46:35 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[17-Apr-2020 13:46:35 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[17-Apr-2020 19:23:22 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[17-Apr-2020 21:17:23 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[17-Apr-2020 21:19:09 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
[17-Apr-2020 21:19:14 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE (`tbl_product`.`product_code` LIKE '%table c%' OR `tbl_product`.`title` LIKE '%table c%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_type` LIKE '%table c%' OR `tbl_product`.`product_key` LIKE '%table c%' OR `PR`.`title` LIKE '%table c%' OR `GP`.`title` LIKE '%table c%') AND `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;

								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

[17-Apr-2020 21:22:54 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

[18-Apr-2020 13:17:14 America/New_York] DB list_count: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `record_count` FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0;
[18-Apr-2020 13:17:14 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[18-Apr-2020 18:56:38 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;

								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`

[18-Apr-2020 19:00:43 America/New_York] DB list_paged: SELECT `tbl_product`.*,
								COALESCE(`PR`.`title`, '') AS `parent`,
								COALESCE(GROUP_CONCAT(`GP`.`title` SEPARATOR ' / '), '') AS `groups`
							 FROM `tbl_product`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `PR` ON `tbl_product`.`parent_id` = `PR`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product_group` `PG` ON `tbl_product`.`product_id` = `PG`.`product_id`
								LEFT OUTER JOIN `tbl_product` `GP` ON `PG`.`group_id` = `GP`.`product_id`
							 WHERE `tbl_product`.`deleted` = 0 GROUP BY `tbl_product`.`product_id` ORDER BY title asc LIMIT 0, 100;
